[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "すべてのビラを配り終えられましたな。\nみんな、お疲れさまでございまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00303",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "科学の時代にチラシ配りなんてと思ったけど……\n悪くない結果だったわ。明後日が楽しみね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00304",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "レスナちゃんもありがとう！\nおかげでもっといいライブになりそうだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00305",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "えへへ。みんなの力になれるなら私も嬉しいから！\n当日までに、錬金術で演出道具を調合しておくね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00306",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ありがとうございまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00307",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "じゃああとは、アタシたちが頑張るだけだね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00308",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "明後日の本番まで、みっちりレッスンよ。\nほら、レッスン室へ行くわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00309",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "またね、レスナちゃん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00310",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "またね、イザナちゃん！　みんな！\n２ｎｄライブ、楽しみにしてるね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00311",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]